Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繞了個大圈子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次由你來說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「喜歡你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,350)}說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(550,350)}不說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,續篇也做得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個遊戲 下一個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是貪便宜買的貨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色可是遊戲的臉啊 這貨沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定是個爛遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找幸運草
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 找到四葉的幸運草了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找的是五葉的幸運草
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有四葉草了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意成為我的葉子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是杉本四葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.99,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be9\an9}毎朝　見かける
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:24.18,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be9\an9}寝癖のあの人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:30.71,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be9\an9}何歳だろう　名前は何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:34.75,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be9\an9}なんか気になる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.99,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be9\an9}每天早上見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:24.18,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be9\an9}那個頭髮睡亂了的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:30.71,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be9\an9}他幾歲了呢 名字叫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:34.75,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be9\an9}總覺得 好在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾露 剩下的我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以幫我去看看桂馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室沒有被用過的痕跡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又通宵玩遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想看到那孩子不可愛的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了 吃早飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 找到什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個等等 早餐怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼我至今為止都沒有遇到這遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 桂木君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道 桂木君也是走這條路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因為今天鬧鐘沒有響 所以稍微遲了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天鬧鐘也不響就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這種地方停下來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 桂木君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為世上 是沒有命運的邂逅的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在我能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的舉止 還有充滿憂鬱的雙瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是那麼完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾去外面玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管好你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四眼宅還是一如既往地噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經覺得那才像桂木呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 興奮過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係 這樣反而能更好地繼續遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:55.40,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.78,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 桂木君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次可以叫你桂馬君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.08,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}可以叫你小四葉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.08,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}可以叫你小四嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.08,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}可以叫你小四甜心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以叫你小四甜心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四甜心？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那樣叫不錯哦 桂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 桂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 桂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四甜心！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包炒麵麵包 還剩一半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神去哪裡了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.15,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊！我忘記帶泳衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:20.81,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:23.01,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿在裡面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神 我找你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很喜歡這個遊戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是玩到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是至今玩過的遊戲中 最接近我理想的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣的話 攻略不是很費時嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你一句名言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神作的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是花時間的少女啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:25.11,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和「穿越時空的少女」音近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確來說 是值得花時間的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是好遊戲 才會想盡量玩久一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟女主角待得更久一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會那樣想也是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四甜心~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩遊戲 所以不能出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大神一入迷就會蹲房裡不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 難得我特意過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次好像特別入迷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我完全沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那是個怎麼樣的遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個這種感覺的女孩出來的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你畫得太菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我覺得挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛 那種塗鴉似的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬君 你喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡我什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這問題…我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道卻還喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好孩子到什麼地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有啊 畫面爛到爆的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准把我的小四甜心當笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有郵件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 現在沒時間看郵件…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B`S ware？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B`S ware！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:38.01,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,0)}{\pos(290,401)}FLAG 12.0 夏日小戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給攻陷之神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近本公司正在製作新GALGAME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 想請素日對GALGAME無比熱情的攻陷之神提點意見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會100%採納
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去製作究極理想的GALGAME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造小四甜心的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想製作100%採納我意見的GALGAME…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想的GALGAME 理想的GALGAME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會像俺所想的那樣去做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的遊戲才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原畫呢 編劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有可愛的女孩子 那樣俺就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹徹底底地做個飽含盛情的遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有10條路線的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深奧而縝密的設定和劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓女孩子更加耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些 遊戲性才重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要稱得上GALGAME 遊戲的樂趣性很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲性？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是邂逅女孩子的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參數什麼的有什麼意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡鬧了 10小時都一直看文章就不是遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是報紙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要吵架嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了屬性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬性才是理想化的極致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的GALGAME 說到底還是音樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你去做三流的爛遊戲吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是越難越好 你這個FLAG狂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵 別吵~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼想哭 就去切洋蔥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 理想的遊戲應該早在腦中構思好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越想就越亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜啊 集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的理想遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位 現在才是變革的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)\pos(440,380)\bord0}在野黨 反單一形式聯合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要將GALGAME的腐敗斬草除根
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每早來叫醒主人公的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬事通的同班男生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一見面就露小褲褲的情節
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提案 把這些情節都廢止！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐敗是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)\pos(470,370)\bord0}執政黨 統一印章畫黨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遵守先人流傳下來的理想傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守舊萬歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止爭吵 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長老
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家 不都是深愛著GALGAME的同志嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼需要爭吵？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是長老
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃課到屋頂和女孩一起吃便當的情節也要廢棄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬君 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺前喝太多水了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神哥哥 在那種地方幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副悲傷的表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GALGAME世紀0079
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單女主角和多女主角的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在此迎接最終局面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬性破壞光線 直擊敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多女主角艦隊 15%被殲滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多女主角的兵器 好像因為BUG用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那堆傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道FLAG管理的難處了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久 多女主角派就會被單女主角派擊潰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 持續數世紀的戰鬥就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真令人悲歎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本該有著相同志向的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今存在著這麼多理想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要統一已經不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究理想也只是現實的一角而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角只要一個就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多的女主角 會稀釋女主角的絕對性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個女主角的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能對應多樣的屬性了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是歪理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有競爭對手 才有劇情發展亮點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你不明白這點？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是詭辯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正確的一方才會贏！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道她名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那個項墜 我也有！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止爭吵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才小四甜心說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GALGAME玩家 大家都是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 為什麼我們會在戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想 從一開始…
