Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏要素 屬性 音樂 限定版手辦都有提到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒提到女孩子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都喜歡著GALGAME
